rows.label: qst200213_msg0001
rows.name:
So, a girl named Harghal commissioned
a job, and I came to collect 3 types
of medicinal herbs, meh.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0002
rows.name: Harghal, you say!?

rows.label: qst200213_msg0003
rows.name: But, what will those herbs be used for?

rows.label: qst200213_msg0004
rows.name:
Herbs are ingredients to make
Pollen Orbs that double
stamina and vigor, meh!

rows.label: qst200213_msg0005
rows.name: Those Pollen Orbs Nopon love, huh.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0006
rows.name:
Though they are prohibited
in some countries.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0007
rows.name: Eh? Is that so?

rows.label: qst200213_msg0008
rows.name:
Pollen Orbs are highly addictive,
and if used too much,
they cause harm to the body.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0009
rows.name:
Therefore, import and export should be
completely prohibited in Superbia?

rows.label: qst200213_msg0010
rows.name: That's exactly right, meh.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0011
rows.name:
Harghal knows it's prohibited
but trades them for a high price, meh.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0012
rows.name:
I see.
You spoke well, Jaruru.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0013
rows.name:
I was struck by your passionate eyes.
I'll stop doing bad jobs forever, meh!

rows.label: qst200213_msg0014
rows.name:
So, where does
the transaction take place?
Harghal is there too, right?

rows.label: qst200213_msg0015
rows.name:
Don't know where
Harghal is right now, meh.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0016
rows.name:
Just, the plan was to mix the gathered
herbs into other cargo and have a
sailor at Ananyam Port transport them.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0017
rows.name:
Ananyam Port[ML:Dash ]
What is that sailor's name?

rows.label: qst200213_msg0018
rows.name: Called Tuvari, meh.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0019
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Uooooh!
Tuvari, prepare yourself!!

rows.label: qst200213_msg0101
rows.name:
Look at my eyes!
These are the eyes of justice!

rows.label: qst200213_msg0102
rows.name:
Look at these eyes and tell
me honestly. Do you have
nothing on your conscience?!

rows.label: qst200213_msg0103
rows.name: N-nothing on my conscience[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200213_msg0104
rows.name:
Really?
Can you swear to your own heart!

rows.label: qst200213_msg0105
rows.name: Uuu[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200213_msg0106
rows.name:
If you have a guilty conscience,
tell me everything.

rows.label: qst200213_msg0107
rows.name:
No matter what happens,
I won't abandon you.
I will save you!

rows.label: qst200213_msg0108
rows.name:
U-uuu[ML:Dash ]
Understood, meh~

rows.label: qst200213_msg0109
rows.name:
Jaruru
will tell everything, meh~
